ay and undeniably fun. You can play for hours and only skim the surface of what this game has to offer... This game is just that damn good." \n\n&#9733 Allemeineapps.de 5/5 \n\n&#9733 iundco.de 90/100\n\n&#9733 TechFever.me 4.5/5 \n\n&#9733 AppSpy 4/5\n\n&#9733 WeDoTech 4.5/5 \n\n------------------------------ \n\nFeed your shark and grow to become the most formidable predator of the seas! But beware... this will soon attract the attention of armed shark hunters both above and below the waves.\n\nGame features:\n&#x2022 Full use of Tilt controls + alternate touch controls\n&#x2022 An ocean full of food and enemies\n&#x2022 Combo eating bonuses\n&#x2022 Lost objects from the world above, find them all for big points\n&#x2022 Hiscore tables: Private and Global, Last 24hrs, Your Country\n&#x2022 Unlock achievements by completing challenges! \n&#x2022 Game Center support - show off your achievements and leaderboard scores to other Game Center friends!', 367835294, 'Future Games of London', ' Games Action Arcade Entertainment', '4.99', 'Hungry Shark Trilogy HD', 406475548, 'com.fgol.HungrySharkTrilogy', '4.2', '2010-12-08T17:45:37Z', 'Games', 1, 'Future Games of London', 6014, '2012-12-22T04:36:50Z', 'iTunes icon fix', ' 6014 7001 7003 6016', '$4.99', '3.5', 578),
