ed control system. Let the tightly tuned physics engine create the most thrilling rides of your life!\n\nPerfect your skills in over 30 tricky rides, from classic wooden coasters to steel speed demons! \n\nUse rockets, Jump jets and magnets, earn hearts and coins, run huge loops, massive jumps and stomach-turning, upside-down tracks!\n\nREVIEWS & PREVIEWS\n\nâ€œ These fluffies are a highly memorable bunch, even if they are a bit nutty.â€\n-Arcade Sushi.com\n\nâ€œA tightly tuned physics engine that underpins some wonderfully silly gameplay.â€\n-Mojodo.com\n\nâ€œNutty Fluffies is simply fun to play thanks to its strangely intuitive physics that make it easy to almost think your way through its challenging stages.â€\n-AppSpy.com\n\nâ€œ Nutty Fluffies offers lots of fun and definitely comes recommended.â€\n-Slide to Play\n\nâ€Intuitive and immediately accessibleâ€ \n-Pocket Gamer\n\n\nCreated by RedLynx:\nThe developer of DrawRace 2, MotoHeroz and Trials Evolution.\n\nCOOL FEATURES\n\nâ€¢Touch-based Gameplay:\nControl your coasters with a simple touch-based interface that controls your gas and brakes. Get ready for new power-ups like rockets, jump-jets and magnets on the most challenging tracks!\n\nâ€¢Wacky Worlds of Wild Rides:\nTake your Fluffies on a tour, from rickety wooden roller coasters to jet-fast joyrides. The Fluffies keep coming back for more fun on Wooden Ways, Metal Mayhem, Loonie Loops, and the extreme Rapture Rides. More to come in updates!\n\nâ€¢Meet the Nutty Fluffies:\nWhen the fair shuts down for the winter, the stuffed animals come out to play! They climb out of their midway booths and take a ride on the wildest roller coasters around!\n\nâ€¢Collect hearts with five unique animals:\nThe Mouse, Cat, Dog, Pig and Elephant will help you to gather hearts and earn coins from the wild rides. Use them to build even longer trains with more carts or unlock exciting new tracks to play!\n\nâ€¢ Wanna ride with no ads? Just buy some coins and they will ALL