('http://is5.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple49/v4/ac/9c/e2/ac9ce224-91f5-c65b-ce52-1896819be52d/source/60x60bb.jpg', 'http://is5.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple49/v4/ac/9c/e2/ac9ce224-91f5-c65b-ce52-1896819be52d/source/100x100bb.jpg', '', ' http://a2.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple49/v4/aa/da/ee/aadaeeb9-cde2-0f90-5f59-b84f3b544399/screen480x480.jpeg http://a1.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple49/v4/bf/6a/ef/bf6aef48-fffe-e9d2-fa54-824588679c20/screen480x480.jpeg http://a3.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple49/v4/0a/97/17/0a9717d2-71f7-34bc-6894-e285ab0783fa/screen480x480.jpeg http://a2.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/13/72/84/137284f8-b51a-33b5-ba3f-ffa6744b5516/screen480x480.jpeg http://a5.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/13/4d/2c/134d2c89-6f47-891d-58ce-59b8fa6a2f3b/screen480x480.jpeg', '', 'http://is5.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple49/v4/ac/9c/e2/ac9ce224-91f5-c65b-ce52-1896819be52d/source/512x512bb.jpg', 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/developer/rusty-moyher/id443831504?uo=4', 'software', '', ' iPad2Wifi iPad23G iPadThirdGen iPadThirdGen4G iPadFourthGen iPadFourthGen4G iPadMini iPadMini4G', ' Infrequent/Mild Cartoon or Fantasy Violence', 0, 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/astro-duel/id548898306?mt=8&uo=4', '9+', 'Astro Duel', 36, 'http://astroduel.com', '4.5', '4', '9+', ' EN', 'USD', 'software', '2.0', 'Astro Duel is a competitive local multiplayer game for iPad and Apple TV.\n\nInspired from endless nights of Super Bomberman, rounds are quick and death is sudden. 2 to 4 players blast each other using asteroid-style ships. The goal: KILL KILL KILL!!\n\n=== Feature List === \n\n13 DYNAMIC ARENAS\nRich, varied arenas provide a host of hiding places and hazards. Use barriers and asteroids as cover. Avoid turrets, death beams, and black holes or you''re dead.\n\nMULTIPLE GAME MODES\nBattle for the most kills in Ship Hunters, outlast your opponents in Pilot Hunters, or join forces in Team Deathmatch.\n\nDEVASTATING POWERUPS\nShips can be armed with offensive and defensive pickups including missiles, lasers, jousters and shields. Race to collect powerups to give yourself an edge or blast powerup-greedy opponents before they reach their prize.\n\niPAD CONTROLS\nUp to 2 players can pilot their ships using just an iPad. No controllers required.\n\niPHONES AS CONTROLLERS\nPilot your ship wirelessly using an iPhone or iPod Touch (with the free Astro Remote app). By using just one iPhone, three players can play simultaneously. Connect more iPhones for more players.\n\nGAMEPAD SUPPORT\nPlay with Bluetooth iOS 7 Controllers like the SteelSeries Stratus. Also supports iCade-compatible controllers and GameDock.\n\nCOMPUTER PLAYERS\nAdd any combination of AI ships. Practice solo against computer-controlled players, mix up free-for-alls, or battle Human vs Machine in a Team Deathmatch. Includes two levels of difficulty.\n\nVARIANTS\nMix up play with a variety of game variants. Start every round with a specific Powerup. Add more asteroids or remove them entirely. Enable or disable fixed spawn, winner''s mini-game, friendly fire, autobalance, start with shield and more.\n\n=== YOUR SHIP A SPLODE ===', 443831504, 'Rusty Moyher', ' Games Arcade Entertainment Action', '4.99', 'Astro Duel', 548898306, 'com.rustymoyher.Astro-Duel', '8.0', '2014-07-24T19:46:14Z', 'Games', 1, 'Rusty Moyher', 6014, '2016-05-05T05:00:25Z', '** Version 2.0 **\n\n3 More Levels\n- Dance\n- Maze\n- Loop\n\n3 More Modifiers\n- No Powerups\n- Unlimited Dash\n- Super Dash\n\nAstro Remote support\n- Pilot your ship with an iPhone or iPod Touch\n- Free download on the App Store\n- Replaces the older Joypad app\n\nCan now cancel a Jouster boost (or the new Super Dash) by pressing the Powerup button\nStarting powerup modifier now shows which powerup is selected before battle. Useful for "Random" starting powerup.\nAdded a new Wild Rooster intro screen\nUpdated the Welcome tutorial with info about the new Astro Remote app\nUpdated the missile powerup artwork\nFixed rare pilot "self-kill" bug\n\nRenamed game mode "Headhunters" to be "Ship Hunters"\nRenamed game mode "Pilot Execution" to be "Pilot Hunters"\nDefault game mode is now Pilot Hunters', ' 6014 7003 6016 7001', '$4.99', '4', 44);
